      }
    },
    "or_image_text_86Ce8e": {
      "type": "or-image-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_DGM3Hb": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Quality + Handmade Craftsmanship //"
          }
        },
        "richtext_qdRQBJ": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Quality and craftsmanship is at the heart of Phoria. Our founder Charlotte comes from a jewellery background and believes it’s important that all Phoria pieces are made from the best materials and are handmade. We only use premium 925 sterling silver and 18ct gold vermeil as well as carefully sourced and selected gemstones.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_nrpX8n": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Each piece is meticulously handcrafted by skilled artisans in Thailand who pour their expertise and passion into each and every piece. Charlotte works closely with them every step of the way and believes in quality over quantity – this ethos is reflected in the detail and care that goes into every Phoria piece.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_hCW9bB": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>An example of this is how our chain bracelets and necklaces are made: each are handmade and assembled link by link with state of the art tools. We do not use off the shelf chain in any of our designs as we take pride in designing and creating every single aspect of our jewellery.</p>"
          }
        },
        "richtext_aCeLDJ": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Before a piece leaves the studio, it’s hallmarked by the Goldsmiths Company Assay Office in London. This means that every piece is officially marked and certified to verify its composition and quality so you can trust that every item you buy from us is made from the finest 925 Sterling Silver.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_DGM3Hb",
        "richtext_qdRQBJ",
        "richtext_nrpX8n",
        "richtext_hCW9bB",
        "richtext_aCeLDJ"
      ],
      "name": "Or-Image-text",
      "settings": {
        "media_position": "left",
